herdr-scratch-pane was originally explored from a tmux-floax-style scratch pane
idea and compared against Tyru5/herdr-floax, which is distributed under the MIT
License.

Reference projects:
https://github.com/Tyru5/herdr-floax
https://github.com/omerxx/tmux-floax

The current implementation uses Herdr native pane rendering and does not copy
the app-drawn terminal renderer from Tyru5/herdr-floax.
